                In <expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>onorem</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>uci</ex></expan> Septimi <lb n="2"/>Severi Pii Pertina<lb break="no" n="3"/>cis <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usti</ex></expan> invicti <expan><abbr>Imp</abbr><ex>eratoris</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/>et <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arci</ex></expan> Aureli Anto<lb break="no" n="5"/>nini <expan><abbr>Caes</abbr><ex>aris</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/>legioni XXII <expan><abbr>Pr</abbr><ex>imigeniae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>iae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ideli</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/>honoris <expan><abbr>virtutisq</abbr><ex>ue</ex></expan> <lb n="8"/>causa civitas Tre<lb break="no" n="9"/>verorum <lb n="10"/>in obsidione ab ea <lb n="11"/>defensa
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Autopsie R. Wiegels. Mittelteil einer Statuenbasis. Das Erhaltene ist in zwei Teile gebrochen. (B): Selzer: Z. 1/2: Zeilenfall nicht angegeben.</p>
